<img src="images/head1a.jpg" width="512" height="161" border="0" alt=""/>
<h2>Straddling the Paradox of Profit and Art, All Chefs must be Mad</h2></div>

<div class="front">

                  <p>
                    For most of us, being a chef is more vocation than job. As artisans we are driven to excellence by a boundless enthusiasm for our craft. Yet no matter how wonderful the end product there is no success without profit.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    Vaulting between the horns of Art and Profit, time is one variable we can manipulate to increase our productivity. The Society of Mad Chefs is striving to provide tools to save the Kitchen Professional time by automating those tedious jobs.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    You can down load any of the files in the <a href="http://www.madchefs.com/forms.htm">Kitchen Forms</a> section or the <a href="http://www.madchefs.com/recipes.htm">Professional Recipes</a> section using the ftp (file transfer protocol) capabilities of your browser of and ftp program such as WS_ftp95 for PCs or fetch for Macintosh. WS_ftp95 is downloadable from your Internet Service Provider or <a href="http://www.davecentral.com/windows.html" target="_blank">DaveCentral.com</a> for windows products and/or <a href="http://www.tucows.com" target="_blank">tucows.com</a> for downloading windows and Mac products.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    In the <a href="http://www.madchefs.com/forms.htm">Chef&rsquo;s Desk</a> section you will find forms for use in a professional kitchen. Most of the Kitchen Forms are in MSExcel and PC format so you will need the Excel spreadsheet program to access those files.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    The <a href="http://www.madchefs.com/recipes.htm">Professional Recipe</a> section has a selection of bulk recipes for use in professional kitchens. In .txt format these files can be viewed then copied and pasted into any format.
                  </p>
                  <p>
                    The <a href="http://www.madchefs.com/placement.htm">Chef Placement</a> section is an affiliate of the Chef Jobs Network. Weather you are looking for Chef Jobs or have a Chef Placement pending The Chef Jobs Network is a bargain.
                  </p>
                  <!-- End  Text -->
</div>
